snippet.title: Friday Night Funkin' VS Skibidi Toilet | Skibidi Invasion [DEMO] (FNF Mod/Hard/Meme)
snippet.description:
Friday Night Funkin' VS Skibidi Toilet | Skibidi Invasion for the PC in 2160p Ultra HD, but this time we take on Skibidi Toilet. Panasco2 - Made everything himself: https://youtu.be/SM3l-OZyQRk

Skibidi dom dom yes yes. Skibidi Invasion is a mod where bf & gf are in the Skibidi toilet universe and has to rap against many friends and foes. Skibidi Toilets are a race of sentient toilets with human heads. They are at war with the Cameramen and The Alliance (Speakerman / Speakermen / TV Man). In a future update, Panasco27 might turn BF & GF into one of those Speakerman. Skibidi Toilet is YouTube Series animated on Source film maker created by DaFuq!?Boom! The series is very popular and is spreading to every corner of YouTube. (The BF & GF are my sprites, the modder is planning on turning them into speakermen so I'll just use my skins in the mean time).

We'll be playing it on very hard against Skibidi Toilet. He only has 1 song called Skibdi in this mod, no game over animation, and 1 week. Can Boyfriend Defeat Skibidi Toilet or will BF lose the battle?

Friday Night Funkin' : Skibidi Invasion DEMO:
https://gamebanana.com/mods/451531

Game Note by Panasco27: This mod was made in a total of ~24 hours
-----
Skibidi Toilet skits | skibidi toilet all episodes by dafuqboom
https://youtu.be/_HuOzlh6mt8

Skibidi - Toilets Attack on the App Store:
https://apps.apple.com/us/app/skibidi-war-toilets-attack/id6449440948
